title: Gustave Caillebotte Paris Street; Rainy Day Puzzle
description:
Allow yourself to be transported by Gustave Caillebotte’s most famous work as you assemble all 1000 pieces of this pensive puzzle. Feel the light splash of raindrops and hear the tapping of bootheels on cobblestone as you are carried back a century to the bustle of a gray Parisian afternoon.

  • Box dimensions: 13 x 10 x 1.88 in.
  • Puzzle dimensions: 25 x 20 in. 
  • Materials: 250 gsm matte art paper; high-quality recycled board
  • Recommended for ages 12 and up
  • 1000 pieces
